== 古生态学 ==
[[File:Hell_Creek_Formation_Fauna.png|500px]]
冥河盗龙是已知最年轻的驰龙科，化石发现于地狱溪组，<ref name="Acheroraptor">{{Cite journal|last1=Evans|first1=D.C.|last2=Larson|first2=D.W.|last3=Currie|first3=P.J.|date=2013|title=A new dromaeosaurid (Dinosauria: Theropoda) with Asian affinities from the latest Cretaceous of North America|url=|journal=Naturwissenschaften|volume=100|issue=11|pages=1041–9|doi=10.1007/s00114-013-1107-5|pmc=|pmid=24248432|bibcode=2013NW....100.1041E}}</ref>该地层的同位素年龄为[[白垩纪-古近纪灭绝事件|白垩纪-古近纪灭绝事件]]前后（约66 ± 0.07百万年前）。<ref name="hcfage">{{Cite journal|last1=Husson|first1=D.E.|last2=Galbrun|first2=B.|last3=Laskar|first3=J.|last4=Hinnov|first4=L.A.|last5=Thibault|first5=N.|last6=Gardin|first6=S.|last7=Locklair|first7=R.E.|date=2011|title=Astronomical calibration of the Maastrichtian (Late Cretaceous)|url=|journal=Earth and Planetary Science Letters|volume=305|issue=3–4|pages=328–340|bibcode=2011E&PSL.305..328H|doi=10.1016/j.epsl.2011.03.008}}</ref>地狱溪组中发现了大量动植物化石，<ref name="weishampel" />其中包括冥河盗龙。其所知于[[暴龙|暴龙]]－[[三角龙|三角龙]]动物群，和体型更大的[[达科他盗龙|达科他盗龙]]一样是最晚出现的驰龙科。<ref name=Acheroraptor /><ref name="DePalmaetal" />

埃文斯等人认为冥河盗龙是地狱溪组中唯一的驰龙科。一些普通牙齿之前归入[[驰龙|驰龙]]和[[蜥鸟盗龙|蜥鸟盗龙]]，之后再次归入冥河盗龙。埃文斯等人推断地狱溪组－兰斯组恐龙组合中可能也仅含这一种驰龙科。<ref name=Acheroraptor />2015年，由于[[达科他盗龙|达科他盗龙]]――一种比该属大得多的第二种驰龙科被叙述，这一观点遭到推翻。<ref name="DePalmaetal">{{cite journal|last1=DePalma|first1=R.A.|last2=Burnham|first2=D.A.|last3=Martin|first3=L.D.|last4=Larson|first4=P.L.|last5=Bakker|first5=R.T.|date=2015|title=The First Giant Raptor (Theropoda: Dromaeosauridae) from the Hell Creek Formation|url=https://kuscholarworks.ku.edu/handle/1808/18764|journal=Paleontological Contributions|volume=|issue=14|pages=1–16|via=|access-date=2020-08-25|archive-date=2015-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151106223159/https://kuscholarworks.ku.edu/handle/1808/18764|dead-url=no}}</ref>该地层中的其它兽脚类包括[[暴龙科|暴龙科]]、[[似鸟龙科|似鸟龙科]]、[[伤齿龙科|伤齿龙科]]、<ref name="weishampel">{{cite book|last=Weishampel|first=D.B.|title=The Dinosauria|url=https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis|url-access=|last2=Dodson|first2=P.|last3=Osmólska|first3=H.|publisher=University of California Press|year=2004|isbn=0520242092|edition=2nd|location=Berkeley, California|pages=[https://archive.org/details/dinosauriandedit00weis/page/n879 861]}}</ref>[[鸟类|鸟类]]、<ref name="pnas">{{Cite journal|last1=Longrich|first1=N.R.|last2=Tokaryk|first2=T.|last3=Field|first3=D.J.|date=2011|title=Mass extinction of birds at the Cretaceous-Paleogene (K-Pg) boundary|url=|journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences|volume=108|issue=37|pages=15253–15257|bibcode=2011PNAS..10815253L|doi=10.1073/pnas.1110395108|pmc=3174646|pmid=21914849}}</ref>和[[近颌龙科|近颌龙科]]。<ref name="Anzu">{{Cite journal|last1=Lamanna|first1=M.C.|last2=Sues|first2=H.D.|last3=Schachner|first3=E.R.|last4=Lyson|first4=T.R.|date=2014|title=A New Large-Bodied Oviraptorosaurian Theropod Dinosaur from the Latest Cretaceous of Western North America|url=|journal=PLOS ONE|volume=9|issue=3|pages=e92022|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0092022|pmc=3960162|pmid=24647078|bibcode=2014PLoSO...992022L}}</ref>该地层中的暴龙科包括[[矮暴龙|矮暴龙]]和暴龙，虽然前者可能是后者的次异名。似鸟龙科包括[[似鸵龙|似鸵龙]]、[[似鸟龙|似鸟龙]]<ref name="weishampel" />和“[[似奥克龙|似奥克龙]]”。<ref name="tb1997">{{cite book|last=Triebold|first=M.|year=1997|chapter=The Sandy site: Small dinosaurs from the Hell Creek Formation of South Dakota|editor-last=Wolberg|editor-first=D.|editor2-last=Stump|editor2-first=E.|editor3-last=Rosenberg|editor3-first=G.|title=Dinofest International: Proceedings of a Symposium Sponsored by Arizona State University Academy of Natural Science|pages=245–248}}</ref>鸟类包括[[鸟龙鸟|鸟龙鸟]]、<ref name="weishampel" />{{link-en|布氏鸟|Brodavis}}、<ref name="brodavis">{{Cite journal|last1=Martin|first1=L.D.|last2=Kurochkin|first2=E.N.|last3=Tokaryk|first3=T.T.|date=2012|title=A new evolutionary lineage of diving birds from the Late Cretaceous of North America and Asia|url=|journal=[[Palaeoworld|Palaeoworld]]|volume=21|pages=59–63|doi=10.1016/j.palwor.2012.02.005}}</ref>和两种未命名的[[黄昏鸟目|黄昏鸟目]]，可能属于{{link-en|河流鸟|Potamornis}}。<ref name="pnas" />地层中只有三种[[偷蛋龙类|偷蛋龙类]]，包括[[安祖龙|安祖龙]]、[[细喙龙属|细喙龙]]<ref name=Anzu />和一件未叙述的标本。此标本非常类似于亚洲的[[巨盗龙|巨盗龙]]，发现于南达科他州，可能是该地层中的第三个偷蛋龙类物种，然而，截至2016年这些标本中仅有脚部化石被叙述。<ref name="http://rmdrc.blogspot.com/2013/12/giant-oviraptor-tracks-from-hell-creek.html">{{cite web|url=http://rmdrc.blogspot.com/2013/12/giant-oviraptor-tracks-from-hell-creek.html|title=Giant Oviraptor Tracks from the Hell Creek|last1=Maltese|first1=A.|date=|website=RMDRC paleo lab|publisher=Blogspot|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112003952/http://rmdrc.blogspot.com/2013/12/giant-oviraptor-tracks-from-hell-creek.html|archive-date=2020-11-12|accessdate=2013-12-17}}</ref>已知的伤齿龙科包括[[伤齿龙|伤齿龙]]、[[梳齿龙|梳齿龙]]和[[近爪牙龙|近爪牙龙]]。该地层中仅含一种可能的[[虚骨龙类|虚骨龙类]]（即[[理查德伊斯特斯龙|理查德伊斯特斯龙]]）。

[[File:Acheroraptor_NT_small.jpg|thumb]]

地狱溪组中存在大量[[鸟臀目|鸟臀目]]，主要分类群包括[[甲龙类|甲龙类]]、[[鸟脚类|鸟脚类]]、[[角龙类|角龙类]]和[[厚头龙类|厚头龙类]]。已发现一种甲龙科和两种结节龙科，包括[[甲龙|甲龙]]、[[丹佛龙|丹佛龙]]和疑似的[[埃德蒙顿甲龙|埃德蒙顿甲龙]]。已知角龙类包括[[纤角龙科|纤角龙科]]的[[纤角龙|纤角龙]]、[[开角龙亚科|开角龙亚科]]的 [[双角龙|双角龙]]、[[牛角龙|牛角龙]]、三角龙<ref name="weishampel" />及[[野牛角龙|野牛角龙]]。<ref name="tatanka">{{cite book|last=Ott|first=C.J.|url=https://www.google.com/books/edition/New_Perspectives_on_Horned_Dinosaurs/OWpQW_WhPAsC?hl=en&gbpv=1&dq=New+Perspectives+on+Horned+Dinosaurs:+The+Royal+Tyrrell+Museum+Ceratopsian+Symposium&printsec=frontcover|title=New Perspectives on Horned Dinosaurs: The Royal Tyrrell Museum Ceratopsian Symposium|last2=Larson|first2=P.L.|publisher=Indiana University Press|year=2010|isbn=9780253353580|editor-last=Ryan|editor-first=M.J.|location=Bloomington|pages=656|chapter=A New, Small Ceratopsian Dinosaur from the Latest Cretaceous Hell Creek Formation, Northwest South Dakota, United States: A Preliminary Description|editor2-last=Chinnery-Allgeier|editor2-first=B.J.|editor3-last=Eberth|editor3-first=D.A.}}</ref>鸭嘴龙类在地狱溪组中很常见，而且种类较多，包括鸟脚类的[[奇异龙|奇异龙]]和[[鸭嘴龙科|鸭嘴龙科]]的[[埃德蒙顿龙|埃德蒙顿龙]]<ref name="weishampel" /><ref name="hcfhadro">{{Cite journal|last1=Campione|first1=N.S.E.|last2=Evans|first2=D.C.|date=2011|title=Cranial Growth and Variation in Edmontosaurs (Dinosauria: Hadrosauridae): Implications for Latest Cretaceous Megaherbivore Diversity in North America|url=|journal=PLOS ONE|volume=6|issue=9|pages=e25186|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0025186|pmc=3182183|pmid=21969872|bibcode=2011PLoSO...625186C}}</ref>和一个未叙述的属，类似[[副栉龙|副栉龙]]。地层中目前已发现五种厚头龙类，包括[[厚头龙科|厚头龙科]]的[[圆头龙|圆头龙]]、[[冥河龙|冥河龙]]、<ref name="weishampel" />[[龙王龙|龙王龙]]、<ref name="bakker">{{cite book|last=Bakker|first=R.T.|last2=Sullivan|first2=R.M.|last3=Porter|first3=V.|last4=Larson|first4=P.|last5=Saulsbury|first5=S.J.|year=2006|chapter=''Dracorex hogwartsia'', n. gen., n. sp., a spiked, flat-headed pachycephalosaurid dinosaur from the Upper Cretaceous Hell Creek Formation of South Dakota|editor-last=Lucas|editor-first=S.G.|editor2-last=Sullivan|editor2-first=R.M.|title=Late Cretaceous vertebrates from the Western Interior|series=New Mexico Museum of Natural History and Science Bulletin|volume=35|pages=331–345|chapter-url=http://econtent.unm.edu/cdm/ref/collection/bulletins/id/710|access-date=2020-08-25|archive-date=2018-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181119203737/http://econtent.unm.edu/cdm/ref/collection/bulletins/id/710|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[厚头龙|厚头龙]]<ref name="weishampel" />及北达科他州一个未叙述的标本。

地狱溪组中的哺乳动物为数众多，具有代表性的分类群包括[[多瘤齿兽目|多瘤齿兽目]]、[[后兽下纲|后兽下纲]]和[[真兽类|真兽类]]。多瘤齿兽目包括{{link-en|Paracimexomys}}、<ref name=":0">{{Cite book|last=Kielan-Jaworowska|first=Z.|title=Mammals from the Age of Dinosaurs: Origins, Evolution, and Structure|last2=Cifelli|first2=R.|last3=Luo|first3=Z-X.|date=2004|publisher=Columbia University Press|year=2004|isbn=9780231119184|location=New York|pages=|oclc=61160163}}</ref>{{link-en|白垩兽科|cimolomyidae}}的{{link-en|Paressonodon}}、<ref name="mammal">{{Cite journal|last1=Wilson|first1=G.P.|date=2013|title=Mammals across the K/Pg boundary in northeastern Montana, U.S.A.: Dental morphology and body-size patterns reveal extinction selectivity and immigrant-fueled ecospace filling|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/paleobiology/article/mammals-across-the-kpg-boundary-in-northeastern-montana-usa-dental-morphology-and-bodysize-patterns-reveal-extinction-selectivity-and-immigrantfueled-ecospace-filling/8CBD705DC009C6F64215B602B043011B|journal=Paleobiology|volume=39|issue=3|pages=429–469|doi=10.1666/12041|via=}}</ref>{{link-en|Meniscoessus}}、{{link-en|Essonodon}}、{{link-en|白垩兽|Cimolomys}}、{{link-en|白垩齿兽|Cimolodon}}以及{{link-en|Cimexomys}}；{{link-en|斜沟齿兽亚目|Neoplagiaulacidae}}的{{link-en|间异兽|Mesodma}}和{{link-en|斜沟齿兽|Neoplagiaulax}}。{{link-en|阿法齿负鼠科|Alphadontidae}}的[[阿法齿负鼠|阿法齿负鼠]]、{{link-en|原阿法齿负鼠|Protalphodon}}和{{link-en|Turgidodon}}。{{link-en|足兽科|Pediomyidae}}的{{link-en|足兽|Pediomys}}、<ref name=":0" />{{link-en|原赖氏兽|Protolambda}}和{{link-en|纤细掠兽|Leptalestes}}，<ref name="mammalshcf">{{Cite journal|last1=Archibald|first1=J.D.|last2=Zhang|first2=Y.|last3=Harper|first3=T.|last4=Cifelli|first4=R.L.|date=2011|title=Protungulatum, Confirmed Cretaceous Occurrence of an Otherwise Paleocene Eutherian (Placental?) Mammal|url=|journal=Journal of Mammalian Evolution|volume=18|issue=3|pages=153–161|doi=10.1007/s10914-011-9162-1}}</ref>{{link-en|Stagodontidae}}的{{link-en|Didelphodon}}，<ref name=":0" />{{link-en|Deltatheridiidae}}的{{link-en|Nanocuris}}，{{link-en|Herpetotheridiidae}}的{{link-en|Nortedelphys}}<ref name="mammal" />和{{link-en|Glasbiidae}}的{{link-en|Glasbius}}等动物皆是地狱溪组有代表性的后兽下纲。地层中已知有大量的真兽类，包括{{link-en|Alostera}}、<ref name=":0" />{{link-en|Protungulatum}}、<ref name="mammalshcf" />{{link-en|白垩掠兽科|Cimolestidae}}的{{link-en|白垩掠兽|Cimolestes}}和{{link-en|Batodon}}，{{link-en|Gypsonictopsidae}}的{{link-en|Gypsonictops}}，可能还有{{link-en|Nyctitheriidae}}的{{link-en|Paranyctoides}}。<ref name=":0" />

